---
title: Crispy Spiced Falafels & Fries with Avocado Salad & Beetroot Relish
description: Make friends with plant-based ingredients by teaming ready-to-cook falafel with some stellar sides: hand cut fries,
beetroot relish and a plant-based mayo perfect for dipping.
